CustomField.description:
This field is invoked when 'Override_Standard_Import_Process__c' is set to true, indicating an override of the standard import process.
The default invoice schedule external id value is mapped to the following field: tc9_pr__Schedule__r.tc9_imp__External_Id_it__c.
